            <p><div class="content_para"><p>This is the current release of the guideline.</p>
<p>This guideline updates a previous version: Fidler JL, Rosen MP, Blake MA, Baker ME, Cash BD, Charron M, Greene FL, Hindman NM, Jones B, Katz DS, Lalani T, Miller FH, Small WC, Sudakoff GS, Tulchinsky M, Yaghmai V, Yee J, Expert Panel on Gastrointestinal Imaging. ACR Appropriateness Criteria&reg; Crohn disease. [online publication]. Reston (VA): American College of Radiology (ACR); 2011. 14 p. [117 references]</p>
<p>This guideline meets NGC's 2013 (revised) inclusion criteria.</p></div></p>
